OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FA man who spent years pretending to be
OL,7,Fseverely disabled to avoid justice
OL,8,Fafter being charged with 15 child sex
OL,9,Foffences against three boys, has been
OL,10,Fjailed for 15 years.
OL,12,FJohn Siddell, 41, was accused of
OL,13,Fsexual assaults against the boys aged
OL,14,Fbetween four and 14.
OL,16,FHe pretended to be non-verbal,
OL,17,Fincapacitated and needing a
OL,18,Fwheelchair, while his brother James
OL,19,FSiddell lied to police about the
OL,20,Fseverity of John's health conditions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FSiddell, 41, formerly from Hinckley,
OL,7,Fwas convicted of perverting the course
OL,8,Fof justice alongside his brother 44-
OL,9,Fyear-old James Siddell, at Leicester
OL,10,FCrown Court on Tuesday 12 May.
OL,12,FBoth brothers refused to attend the
OL,13,Fhearing and were sentenced in their
OL,14,Fabsence.
OL,16,FJudge Keith Raynor sentenced John
OL,17,FSiddell to nine years and two months
OL,18,Fin prison with an extended licence
OL,19,Fperiod of two years. He was also given
OL,20,Fa 15-year-old Sexual Harm Prevention
OL,21,FOrder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FJames Siddell was sentenced to two
OL,7,Fyears and nine months in prison.
OL,9,FThe judge described the pair as
OL,10,F"deceitful and devious" and that they
OL,11,F"entirely corrupted the course of
OL,12,Fjustice".
OL,14,FThe brothers' deception came to light
OL,15,Fwhen the officer in charge of the case
OL,16,Fsaw John Siddell behaving normally
OL,17,Fwithout his wheelchair, moments before
OL,18,Fhe saw his solicitor.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FThe officer then decided to look back
OL,7,Fat CCTV and found footage which showed
OL,8,FJohn Siddell going about his daily
OL,9,Flife without a wheelchair, and only
OL,10,Fpretending to be incapacitated and
OL,11,Fmute when he was with police or other
OL,12,Fauthorities, or the day before he was
OL,13,Fdue to attend court.
OL,15,FHow did the case unfold?
OL,17,FPolice first received reports of child
OL,18,Fsex offences committed by John Siddell
OL,19,Fin June 2021.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FAt the time of the reporting of the
OL,7,Foffences in June, the boys were aged
OL,8,F8, 10 and 13. But the abuse had been
OL,9,Fgoing on for two-years prior to that.
OL,11,FIn July and November 2021, John was
OL,12,Finterviewed by police but refused to
OL,13,Fanswer any questions.
OL,15,FThe brothers then moved from
OL,16,FLeicestershire to Northumberland.
OL,18,FBy June 2022, John had been charged
OL,19,Fwith 15 offences against three boys.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FThe brothers then spent the next year
OL,7,Ffalsely claiming that John suffered
OL,8,Ffrom a number of physical and
OL,9,Fpsychological conditions, all while
OL,10,Fpolice and the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService were preparing for trial.
OL,13,FIn February 2023, just days before a
OL,14,Fcourt hearing, James requested a
OL,15,Fletter from John's GP to excuse John
OL,16,Ffrom attending, saying he was not well
OL,17,Fenough to travel.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FIn March 2023, John missed a court-
OL,7,Fordered assessment, prompting the
OL,8,Fcourt to order an assessment to
OL,9,Fdetermine John's fitness to stand
OL,10,Ftrial.
OL,12,FAssessments took place in April and
OL,13,FJune 2023, where John presented
OL,14,Fhimself as both mute and immobile.JIn
OL,15,FJune 2023, the court ruled that John
OL,16,Fwas unfit to plead or stand trial.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FA trial of facts was held at Leicester
OL,7,FCrown Court in March 2024, where John
OL,8,Fwas found to have committed 17 child
OL,9,Fsex offences.
OL,11,FThe court then ordered a further
OL,12,Fassessment before an outcome would be
OL,13,Fdecided.
OL,15,FJust before a meeting on 29th April
OL,16,F2024, DC Gibson saw John upright and
OL,17,Falert in his wheelchair, but when he
OL,18,Fentered the meeting room, he was mute
OL,19,Fand immobile with his eyes closed. At
OL,20,Fthis point, DC Gibson started to
OL,21,Finvestigate further.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FOver the next 18 months, DC Gibson
OL,7,Fcollected evidence which revealed
OL,8,FJohn's health conditions were made up
OL,9,For exaggerated.
OL,11,FIn July 2024, the two brothers were
OL,12,Farrested for perverting the course of
OL,13,Fjustice and were released under
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FA year later, both were charged with
OL,17,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
