PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778836033
OL,3,CMan who faked being severely disabled
OL,4,Cto avoid child sex charges is jailed
OL,6,FIn September 2025, both men pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to perverting the course of
OL,8,Fjustice. John pleaded guilty to 15 of
OL,9,Fthe child sex offences.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
